com.github.moribund.objects.nonplayable.projectile

Class ProjectileBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.moribund.objects.nonplayable.projectile.ProjectileBuilder

  • public final class ProjectileBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    The ProjectileBuilder follows the Builder pattern to allow for an easy-to-use API to create a rather-complex object: a Projectile.
